{
  "stem": "5313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And at that time, you know, Montgomery was, you know, general at the English zone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And his secretary, I happened to know her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I could give words what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And within 24 hours, they sent us help, you know, when we get out of the jail and I went back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a little excitement, but I did it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Tell us a little about your life in Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Frankfurt was already-- I went into a Germany home which at that time still was not occupied.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A few friends of ours and we occupied a house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we was living a pretty normal life over there, already started even for the Germans getting back into normal life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it wasn't anything that any other people would do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We was doing, like I said, a little black marketing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we have enough money already to live fairly good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's what I--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- sort of a work?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just working for ourselves, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We tried to do what we can, you know, to make some money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there until 1949.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1949, it was started to have, for myself, a little problem with the Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While we was stealing, you know, we felt that we had rights to do a lot of bad things for them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it wasn't exactly that way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, they started to get in a normal life, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I say, you know, this is the time for me to get back and get out of there.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
